              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Leonard uses many times the motif, taken from William Blake, of the struggling prophet saddled with cheap and vulgar instruments. Here the angel is saddled with the poor instrument, while the devil has a harp. It suggests a social arrangement where the most beautiful voices may be leading us astray."
